WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:04.278
Hey, good morning family, praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us.

00:00:04.279 --> 00:00:10.039
It's Diana and Brandon again, the dynamic duo. I'm excited to be here, baby.

00:00:10.040 --> 00:00:19.646
I have some things on my heart, and I know you do. We were talking about it today and what we feel in the atmosphere.

00:00:19.648 --> 00:00:30.283
You can feel there's a tangible feeling that something is about to happen, like a puzzle you just focus on and try to figure out all the pieces, and it's too hard.

00:00:30.284 --> 00:00:48.863
So you just have to focus on the piece that you have in your hand, praying that piece through instead of thinking about the whole, like, 'Well, this is overwhelming, all of this needs prayer.'You just focus on one piece at a time, the piece that's right in front of you, and you pray that through.

00:00:48.864 --> 00:00:58.213
And when that piece goes in and you see it go into the puzzle, then He'll hand you another piece and you just pray over that piece and you keep doing it until the whole picture's done.

00:00:58.214 --> 00:01:10.712
Sometimes we just get overwhelmed in prayer thinking about how this is a mess, this whole puzzle needs this, and I can't even see what it's going to be like.

00:01:10.713 --> 00:01:14.135
You don't even know what the picture is or where we are going right now.

00:01:14.136 --> 00:01:31.544
And that's where I felt like when I'm praying, I asked, 'What is priority number one, Lord, on Your heart?'Because right now the canvas she's talking about, this massive canvas, this puzzle, is overwhelming.

00:01:31.545 --> 00:01:48.079
I was praying over it, and I know that what I have right now, what I've seen in the spirit and what I saw in a video back, is another storm—a major shaking to awaken is coming, you all.

00:01:48.080 --> 00:01:59.898
After I stopped praying with you, I prayed for at least another hour, praying into that because the spirit of intercession hit me so hard.

00:01:59.899 --> 00:02:08.192
It was so heavy. I came in, sat on the couch, and I started hearing prophetically about our life.

00:02:08.193 --> 00:02:13.522
The Lord just started downloading again, warning us of what's coming.

00:02:13.523 --> 00:02:24.068
I saw a rectangular window before me in the spirit realm, and the Lord told me there is going to be a window of blessing.

00:02:24.069 --> 00:02:45.586
I'm telling you, you can see it right now, that what I saw about the economy crash is trying to manifest right in front of our faces, but the Lord is saying if we would pray and seek His face, He would give us this window of opportunity for the wealth of the wicked to be laid up for the righteous.

00:02:45.587 --> 00:03:02.358
We need this for the harvest; we need this wealth transfer. Listening to Him on a day-to-day basis, listening to Him on what to do with your finances, because God is going to be a rewarder of those that diligently seek Him.

00:03:02.359 --> 00:03:17.665
I don't believe it's for us to go into this crash of what I've seen coming with nothing and be there going, 'How are we going to do this?'I believe it's going to be a surplus on the body of Christ.

00:03:17.666 --> 00:03:23.687
For what I have seen, I told you, a remnant will walk in the blessing.

00:03:23.688 --> 00:03:31.439
I saw a one percent margin, and they go, 'Well, you know, that's not enough.'Well, one percent out of a billion is pretty good.

00:03:31.440 --> 00:03:39.238
I mean, I don't know, that's a lot of folks. I don't know the math on it exactly, but I'm just saying that's a lot.

00:03:39.239 --> 00:03:52.729
So I'm not going to say the sky is falling, but I've told you all, I have seen a major economic shaking that is worse than the 1920s or 1930s, worse than the Great Depression.

00:03:52.730 --> 00:04:04.085
It was the Great Depression on steroids. I'm talking very bad looting, rioting, and pillaging like we've never seen before.

00:04:04.086 --> 00:04:15.182
People act crazy because it's not like it was in the thirties; people have no morals like they did then, some common sense.

00:04:15.183 --> 00:04:25.514
I saw places of refuge again. The Lord spoke about places having water. I saw a great drought again.

00:04:25.515 --> 00:04:36.218
I saw great manipulation with the weather again, and I thought it was very interesting because I was watching Benny Johnson's video about the JFK files.

00:04:36.219 --> 00:04:48.886
My son, my wife, and I were all watching it, and we were like, 'Oh dear God,'at how corrupt the CIA was back in the sixties.

00:04:48.887 --> 00:05:09.779
It was overwhelming, really, some of the things that were being said and what he was reading in the transcripts from those 80,000-page reports about Israel, the nuclear capabilities, and setting up governments with all kinds of dirtiness.

00:05:09.780 --> 00:05:20.379
It was bad stuff; I was embarrassed as a citizen of the United States of America to hear that coming from our government, how corrupt they were even in the sixties.

00:05:20.380 --> 00:05:32.173
I was like, 'Wow, my dad was a little boy; this is really bad.'I'm just saying folks, it's eye-opening.

00:05:32.174 --> 00:05:44.048
And weather manipulation—they were using weather trying to figure out how to use weather manipulation to dethrone governments. This is what I've been praying over.

00:05:44.049 --> 00:05:56.076
I've told you all that they're going to use weather manipulation like we've never seen it before, and there will be drought in some areas and rain in another.

00:05:56.077 --> 00:06:10.159
It's going to be very serious drought and very serious floods. All that to say, I'm not afraid of it. I have total peace.

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:18.965
Whenever people say, 'Are you tormented when you see these things?'No, I have total peace. I don't even let it get to me.

00:06:18.966 --> 00:06:42.407
I just go, 'This isn't about me; this is about a shaking.'If I let my flesh look at it in the natural, yeah, you could get freaked out, but I stay spiritual about it and I stay in the spirit, praying in tongues over it.

00:06:42.408 --> 00:07:03.136
When the Lord shows me the things to come and warns you about these things, it's not for me to sound the alarm in fear like 'Chicken Little, the sky is falling.'There's going to be a great economic crisis and people are going to stand in food lines for miles long.

00:07:03.137 --> 00:07:13.416
I'm saying it as a watchman seeing it, and I refuse to fear it because I have peace.

00:07:13.417 --> 00:07:34.742
You know when it's the Spirit of the Lord warning you about something versus the devil coming and tormenting you, it's when you have the peace that passes understanding while looking into something that should scare you, something that should make you crawl in a fetal position and rock.

00:07:34.743 --> 00:07:38.918
Does that freak me out right now when I'm telling you this? No. Why?

00:07:38.919 --> 00:07:44.336
Because I'm hearing the Spirit of the Lord warn me about something that's coming.

00:07:44.337 --> 00:07:51.516
When I see the plague and I see the people all on the cots, and I've seen all these things, was I in fear over that?

00:07:51.517 --> 00:07:58.598
No, not even a little bit, because I'm seeing it by the prophetic eye, the watchman eye.

00:07:58.599 --> 00:08:16.743
What the Lord's warned me about the plagues coming, I say none of that comes near me because He said if you stand on Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 and you get that down as a pillar in your heart, that no weapon formed against you will prosper.

00:08:16.744 --> 00:08:25.651
That's where we stay. We walk through the valley of the shadow of death, but we will fear no evil regardless of the plague, regardless of the pestilence.

00:08:25.651 --> 00:08:50.103
And the Lord showed me, He said, 'Brandon, America will be humbled.'That's not a word I want to tell everybody, but He said the church, the people, have a stiff neck towards Me, and in this, there will be a shaking to awaken again.

00:08:50.104 --> 00:09:00.479
I was looking at the hearts upon the land, and all of a sudden, all the hearts became one heart.

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:08.558
It was very strange, but I could see all the hearts of the church and the nation, and all of them became one heart.

00:09:08.559 --> 00:09:22.639
The heart was black-looking and it had blood flowing from it. The center was starting to turn black.

00:09:22.640 --> 00:09:29.599
There was a little red left, but it was trying to turn into a black heart.

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:37.671
What does that mean? I don't know. I see it and I pray over it, but it is alarming to me.

00:09:37.672 --> 00:09:46.546
It wasn't just one heart, one person; it was a vast majority of hearts, and it all became one heart.

00:09:46.547 --> 00:09:54.606
There was a little sliver of red in the middle, and all around it looked like it was toxic.

00:09:54.607 --> 00:10:05.864
The further it went out, it was black, and then it went into gray and then red.

00:10:05.865 --> 00:10:11.133
That's what I saw in the spirit. I haven't said that to anybody; even my family didn't know that.

00:10:11.134 --> 00:10:22.903
Some things I pray and I go, 'Oh, I probably should say that,'but that's what I saw.

00:10:22.904 --> 00:10:28.569
Then I saw the people with their noses stuck up and their necks were stiff.

00:10:28.570 --> 00:10:31.762
That's why I call them stiff-necked, because their necks were stiff.

00:10:31.763 --> 00:10:49.772
They were all upon the land and He said, 'A great humbling is coming,'but I'm giving you a window for My beloved, for My remnant, so that this will not affect you if you're listening to Me.

00:10:49.773 --> 00:11:10.748
If you remember, Abraham interceded on behalf of Lot. Lot did not know that judgment was coming because he was living there and he was amongst them.

00:11:10.749 --> 00:11:23.846
Because he had become lukewarm and become part of Sodom and Gomorrah in the way they thought, he did not know that in a 24-hour period judgment was coming.

00:11:23.847 --> 00:11:43.936
So God sent an angelic host to go and get Lot and his family out of that hellhole, and he grabbed a hold of them because of intercessory prayer. Abraham interceded on behalf of Lot.

00:11:43.937 --> 00:12:02.322
My point is that many are Lots; many are in the cities and they don't know it because they've become so complacent and lukewarm that they're in the midst of it, and it's going to take an intercessor to pull you out by the grace of God.

00:12:02.323 --> 00:12:22.605
That's why I'm a watchman. That's why I sit on my perch and I come on here to warn you that God said there will be a major shaking over America, but He's given you a window.

00:12:22.606 --> 00:12:28.382
There's something greater, something deeper to the meaning of this four-year window.

00:12:28.383 --> 00:12:40.286
It's big. This is the beginning of what I believe is the tribulation.

00:12:40.287 --> 00:12:49.952
He keeps speaking to me about this four-year window and I keep praying into it—a harvest of souls.

00:12:49.952 --> 00:13:05.736
Even Diana said, 'Brandon, I heard what you said about the harvest.'You said a financial crash will happen and then the harvest, a plague will happen, and all these things.

00:13:05.737 --> 00:13:12.227
But what brings the harvest? What is the trigger to the mechanism of the harvest?

00:13:12.228 --> 00:13:23.198
I saw a financial crisis throughout the whole world, I saw a plague, and I saw people running.

00:13:23.199 --> 00:13:27.237
What gets their attention? What shakes them out of their sleep?

00:13:27.238 --> 00:13:36.447
Touching their money, touching their circumstances; that's what shakes them out of it.

00:13:36.448 --> 00:13:45.681
I saw another major attack coming to America. I saw great shakings. I saw the enemy within again.

00:13:45.682 --> 00:14:00.518
I saw 'Red Dawn'again, praying over that, with a major uprising of these ants inside our country.

00:14:00.519 --> 00:14:11.155
I don't know what that is; I keep seeing it. So let's pray. I'm praying into the financial outpouring. We see the stock markets; we see what's happening.

00:14:11.156 --> 00:14:36.873
I told you, if they would go to that extent to eliminate JFK, how much more are they trying to bring down the dollar for the beast system, for a one-world order?

00:14:36.874 --> 00:14:49.058
Who is over all of this? Who's the boss? The devil. I told you I saw him strategically talking to major banking men and people in government.

00:14:49.059 --> 00:15:05.422
He was talking to them, the George Soroses, the Bill Gateses. He was influencing them, and they didn't realize it.

00:15:05.423 --> 00:15:17.636
I'm not going to say every one of them is having satanic practices, but I saw him influencing these men with great wealth.

00:15:17.637 --> 00:15:36.382
The Lord told me you do not get to that high level of wealth without a satanic agenda right now in the world; there's some demonic force feeding that because that's Satan's wheelhouse.

00:15:36.383 --> 00:15:51.236
So we're praying for the finances for the body of Christ, for the outpouring, for whatever the Holy Spirit wants us to pray for right now.

00:15:51.237 --> 00:15:55.040
We're going to pray for about 30 minutes unless the Holy Spirit leads us to go longer.

00:15:55.041 --> 00:16:23.722
We believe in the baptism of the Holy Spirit and we go into the throne boldly.

00:16:23.723 --> 00:16:30.129
I'm going to believe that God's going to show us things to come as a watchman today.

00:16:30.130 --> 00:16:55.177
Diana and I are going to do that, and if you see anything, tap me and let me know.

00:16:55.178 --> 00:16:59.758
Father, we thank You right now. We come before Your throne boldly.

00:16:59.759 --> 00:17:07.569
We take back what the enemy stolen from us. We believe, Father, for the 30, 60, and 100-fold return.

00:17:07.570 --> 00:17:11.124
We believe that everything we put our hands to will prosper.

00:17:11.125 --> 00:17:24.300
We take authority over the spirit of poverty and lack over our households, and we say, 'Thus far and no further!'You release our finances now in the name of Jesus.

00:17:24.301 --> 00:17:32.528
We call millions of dollars into the kingdom of God to flow through our hands.

00:17:32.529 --> 00:17:40.759
We believe that You're able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:17:40.760 --> 00:17:46.630
We thank You, Lord, that the angels are going from the north, south, east, and west to bring the harvest in.

00:17:46.631 --> 00:18:14.056
We call in the harvest; we call in the lost, the ones in the very back field where it looks hopeless.

00:18:14.057 --> 00:18:20.558
You said give them one last call. We thank You, Lord, that there's a shaking to awaken.

00:18:20.559 --> 00:18:44.199
Every single one of them would have their eyes opened. We say in the name of Jesus, Satan, get your hands off of these unsaved loved ones! We call their eyes flooded with light.

00:18:44.200 --> 00:19:03.538
They would have a Damascus Road experience, a supernatural experience so they would understand there's a God that loves them and they would have a choice to serve the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:19:03.539 --> 00:19:37.229
You choose life or death, heaven or hell. I pray it's the right choice.

00:19:37.230 --> 00:19:50.427
Father, I thank You that they will not have any demonic interference to make that choice, that their eyes would be opened and they would see the lies from the pit of hell.

00:19:50.428 --> 00:20:41.242
It is a no-brainer to serve the Lord Jesus Christ. I thank You that their eyes would see how good You truly are, for You are good and Your mercy endures forever.

00:20:41.243 --> 00:21:01.198
Holy Spirit, work on their hearts today in the middle of their despair and agony. Draw them close to You, Father.

00:21:01.199 --> 00:21:06.558
We thank You for Your supernatural outpouring over the United States and around the world.

00:21:06.559 --> 00:22:20.719
We call forth revival from coast to coast. Holy Spirit, we yield ourselves.

00:22:20.720 --> 00:23:31.359
Flow through us. We ask You to show us that which is to come. I hear this: He said take communion.

00:23:31.360 --> 00:23:46.510
Father, we enter in by the blood, by this covenant. We thank You that we enter in by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony. We lift it up before You.

00:23:46.511 --> 00:24:01.619
He was wounded for our transgressions, He was bruised for our iniquities, the chastisement of our peace was upon Him, and with His stripes we are healed.

00:24:01.620 --> 00:24:22.075
We're going to walk in divine health and divine wealth. We take this body in the name of Jesus and thank You, Lord, that what You bore in Your body we need not bear in our own.

00:24:22.076 --> 00:24:48.708
We're healed and whole and well because You said it, Lord. Every good and perfect thing comes from the Father of Light.

00:24:48.709 --> 00:25:04.835
We take this blood in the name of Jesus and thank You for it. We apply the blood of Jesus over our sins.

00:25:04.836 --> 00:26:24.829
Now we enter into that throne by the blood. He says it's a dance.

00:26:24.830 --> 00:26:49.088
You don't rush the dance. It's a dance where one leads and one follows.

00:26:49.089 --> 00:28:44.079
He's leading, we follow. I see the ballroom. Don't be in a hurry; just let it flow.

00:28:44.080 --> 00:30:22.807
The symphony is beautiful. Intimacy is gentle. Get an inward image of what you're praying for today.

00:30:22.808 --> 00:30:33.065
See it in the eye and pray toward it. Don't just pray aimlessly; put your faith towards it.

00:30:33.066 --> 00:31:08.373
Visualize it inside and pray over it. Right now, we push for the finances of America, for the outpouring of finances.

00:31:08.374 --> 00:32:37.793
When you're praying in tongues, push it toward the outpouring. If we push together, we make much progress.

00:32:37.794 --> 00:33:04.079
We pray as a body and push as an army—focused, precision, pinpoint prayer.

00:33:04.080 --> 00:33:19.434
It's like lifting weights; we're grabbing and pulling that rope, moving stones out of the way to clear the road together.

00:33:19.435 --> 00:35:44.807
We seek You first, Lord. Seek ye first the kingdom and all these things will be added unto us. Seek My face, He says. Sit in My lap today. Abide in Me.

00:35:44.808 --> 00:36:22.809
