00:36:22.810 --> 00:36:41.690
Don't be out of balance with the finances; be in balance with Me.

00:36:41.691 --> 00:38:41.342
Seek My face and you can have what's in My hand. I will open the doors.

00:38:41.343 --> 00:39:16.239
It's back to the dance. As He leads, we follow. We will not get out of step.

00:39:16.240 --> 00:39:52.903
There's intimacy in the seeking. It's seeking the face of God.

00:39:52.904 --> 00:40:04.358
Seek Me, and I will give all unto you as I see that you can handle it.

00:40:04.359 --> 00:40:13.532
As you go from glory to glory, some are bridled and can handle it, but there are many that can't.

00:40:13.533 --> 00:40:31.860
So I wait and I watch for the heart that is after Me. As the heart panteth for the water brooks, so does my soul longeth after You.

00:40:31.861 --> 00:40:51.616
In the seeking, you lose yourself in Him. Nothing else matters.

00:40:51.617 --> 00:41:12.566
That's when the transfer happens—when you're dead to self.

00:41:12.567 --> 00:41:45.309
Many seek the money, but He says lose yourself in Me. When you are dead to self, it's a fragrance of beauty to Me.

00:41:45.310 --> 00:42:27.625
There's no faking death. When I know that you're yielded, it keeps you on that straight and narrow.

00:42:27.626 --> 00:42:55.438
Many of you are not ready for this wealth transfer, which is why I have said only one percent.

00:42:55.439 --> 00:43:26.946
I must be first, and wealth is a tool. Many are out of balance, seeking money with a divided heart.

00:43:26.947 --> 00:43:52.013
I'll have all of you or none of this. Seek Me, and in this, I will give it to you.

00:43:52.014 --> 00:44:21.310
Losing yourself in My face today. I keep seeing that He's a jealous God who desires us to be on fire.

00:44:21.311 --> 00:44:45.528
Many are lukewarm, seeking money with ulterior motives, not falling in love with the King.

00:44:45.529 --> 00:45:11.879
He sees the church with one foot in the world and one foot over here.

00:45:11.880 --> 00:45:39.251
I desire for you to have all of it. As you die to self, you will be entrusted with greater wealth.

00:45:39.252 --> 00:45:55.719
But you're running out of time. There will be levels of wealth.

00:45:55.720 --> 00:46:07.018
Many will stay down here and eat crumbs, but many will go up here and flow, funneling the crumbs.

00:46:07.019 --> 00:47:51.352
It's a process of keeping your lamps full. He is a holy God and will not allow this. He sees the intent of man.

00:47:51.353 --> 00:48:50.395
I will give you hidden treasures, riches stored in secret places, so that you may know that I am the Lord, the God of Israel, who summons you by name.

00:48:50.396 --> 00:49:32.562
The greater wealth transfer is a trusted thing. As you lose yourself in Him, He will show you the hidden treasures of Isaiah 45.

00:49:32.563 --> 00:50:48.409
Once you touch that hem, all the earthly stuff—the cars, the houses—nothing else matters but the glory.

00:50:48.410 --> 00:52:01.737
I am the Lord, and there is no other. Money is not your God. I form the light and create darkness; I bring prosperity and create disaster.

00:52:01.738 --> 00:53:02.419
I, the Lord, do all these things. Money is a tool, but I will not share My place.

00:53:02.420 --> 00:53:05.687
It's like the spoiled rich kid who loves on their dad just to get the keys to the car.

00:53:05.688 --> 00:53:50.890
He sees the motive of the heart. That's why He said only one percent—they've lost themselves in Me.

00:53:50.891 --> 00:55:04.275
It took the dance of the last many years. You cannot fake death; the odor gives it away. A person who is ready is a fragrance at the altar.

00:55:04.276 --> 00:56:02.612
I saw many in this vision grabbing fragments off the ground from the ones who were dead, funneling it down because they didn't care about it; all they cared about was Him.

00:56:02.613 --> 00:57:31.018
