00:57:40.205 --> 00:58:30.318
All I need is Him. He doesn't care if you have houses or cars, as long as they don't have you.

00:58:30.319 --> 00:58:47.325
He is a jealous God that wants all of us. He doesn't want your leftovers.

00:58:47.326 --> 00:59:30.290
Give Him your first. Don't give Him old, tired days. Relationship is maintaining that connection all day long.

00:59:30.291 --> 00:59:37.545
I pray this video blessed you. I appreciate the vision the Lord showed me.

00:59:37.546 --> 01:00:08.407
I give You all the glory, Father. Thank You for the correction and guidance.

01:00:08.408 --> 01:00:22.399
Thank You that You love me enough to rebuke me. Spank me, Lord, so that I would be better.

01:00:22.400 --> 01:01:14.279
We love You and praise You. Thank You for Isaiah 45. We will seek You and find You.

01:01:14.280 --> 01:01:24.354
Whatever You desire, we lose ourselves in You. You lead, we follow.

01:01:24.355 --> 01:01:43.435
I feel the presence of the Lord so strong. Jesus is wonderful.

01:01:43.436 --> 01:01:59.706
He said, 'Don't get in a rush, don't push it; dance.'He was rebuking me because I try to rush.

01:01:59.707 --> 01:02:29.249
No, dance, Brandon, just be at peace. Sit at My feet. I'll take these treasures and use them for the rest of my life.

01:02:29.250 --> 01:02:36.469
These are moments for me. We bless you all. Subscribe, click the notification bell, and comment something nice.

