01:03:51.924 --> 01:03:59.653
Jesus Christ is coming back for a glorious church without spot or wrinkle.

01:03:59.655 --> 01:04:27.038
You're part of the remnant. Focus on Him. Lose yourself in Him, and He'll give you everything.

01:04:27.039 --> 01:05:32.429
I want to be a person used by You, Father. We always humble ourselves before You.

01:05:32.430 --> 01:06:23.343
